snippet.title: F.A.H. (Amber Heard Diss) - Slim Vanilla (Ft. Allen Gun)
snippet.description:
Happy Birthday Bitch
Cover Art By @ gangsterartz
F.A.H. – Slim Vanilla (Ft. Allen Gun)

Chorus: (Slim Vanilla, Allen Gun)

Fuck Amber Heard (X8)

Verse: (Slim Vanilla)

Fuck you Amber Hear if you got beat then you deserved it
There’s a special seat for you in hell I heard Satan reserved it
Everybody wants this bitch begone you know we would prefer it
You’re an actress but can’t fake abuse well you ain’y selling shit
I hate your fucking guts but I would smash for the hell of it
Fuck you Amber Heard what you did is absurd
Middle fingers up to you bitch call that a flock of birds
Fuck you Amber Heard you just lying for the bands
If I ever see you, you gone catch these Edward fucking Scissor Hands
You don’t got fans karmas got plans ain’t nobody stans and I don’t understand
How people believe in this bullshit when the proofs in the palm of their hands
Bitch you just be lying for dinero
Pinocchio nose long and narrow
I’m ruthless I’m a pirate no Jack Sparrow

Pre-Chorus: (Slim Vanilla, Allen Gun)

Fuck you Amber Heard what you did is absurd
Middle fingers up to you bitch call that a flock of birds (X2)

Verse: (Allen Gun)

Slim Vanilla man I hate this bitch like hella man
“Boogeyman Style” scary and wild
I hate a bum bitch who lies like a child
Animosity your hypocrisy slit your throat exposed bitch you lost you see?
You ain’t shit to me 
D-List maybe
Bullshit celebrity
Hang your ass from a tree
Fuck with johnny bitch I’ll gut your body bitch
Leave you in a box call me Roddy Rich bitch
Fuck it I’m so outta breath
Getting this anna all off of my chest
Amber you best make your peace with your maker because that is who you will be seeing next
Seen them tapes
Ain’t no escape
Truth is out it’s the end of your days
Cult Of The Void on that Helter Skelter shit we’ll kill your ass like Sharron Tate

Verse: (Slim Vanilla)

Fuck you Amber I’m all for slander
No respect for you bitch don’t got manners
Discreditable unethical actions toxic like chemical
I’ll show you abuse and we’ll see if it’s identical
You a clown no Heath Ledger and I think it’s hysterical
I’ll beat your ass not being hypothetical
Damage is done
It’s too late
You a bitch and a liar not up for debate
I said what I said and I done what I done
Now theres just one thing I gotta say bitch

Pre-Chorus: (Slim Vanilla, Allen Gun)

Fuck you Amber Heard what you did is absurd
Middle fingers up to you bitch call that a flock of birds (X2)

Chorus: (Slim Vanilla, Allen Gun)

Fuck Amber Heard (X8)
